tface-killah@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ghostface-killah@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ghostface-killah@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ghostface-killah@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wu-tang-clan">Wu-Tang Clan</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghostface-killah">Ghostface Killah</a>已确认他将于明年发行一本新的回忆录，名为“Rise Of A Killah：我的 Wu-Tang 生活”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读</b><b>更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/gods-of-rap-uk-tour-london-wembley-arena-review-wu-tang-clan-public-enemy-de-la-soul-dj-premier-2486728"><b>说唱之神巡演：武当派统治至高无上，公敌和德拉灵魂回溯岁月</b></a></li></ul><p>即将出版的回忆录已通过其出版商麦克米伦出版社宣布，预计将于明年 5 月 14 日发行。该书目前提供三种格式的预订：精装书、电子书和数字音频。 <a href="https://us.macmillan.com/books/9781250274274/rise-of-a-killah" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订《Rise Of A Killah》</a> 。</p><p>根据麦克米伦的网站，《基拉的崛起：我的武当生涯》被描述为“既是表演者生活的视觉记录，又是真实的叙述”。</p><p>这本回忆录似乎记录了这位说唱歌手在斯塔顿岛的童年、他与家人和朋友的关系、犯罪和暴力如何影响他的生活、他的艺术、90年代在日本的一次成长之旅以及他的武当成员同伴。 </p><figure id="attachment_3377679" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3377679" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3377679" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Ghostface-Killah.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="鬼脸基拉。图片来源：Daniel Knighton，盖蒂图片社" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Ghostface-Killah.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Ghostface-Killah.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Ghostface-Killah.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Ghostface-Killah.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Ghostface-Killah.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Ghostface-Killah.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3377679" class="wp-caption-text">鬼脸基拉。图片来源：Daniel Knighton，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>通过《Rise Of A Killah》，鬼面将成为武当派最新一位发行回忆录的成员。 2021年，Raekwon发行了《从楼梯到舞台：Raekwon和武当派的故事》，而U-God则于2018年发行了《Raw：我的武当派之旅》。</p><p> Wu-Tang Clan 今年庆祝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wu-tang-clan-album-enter-the-wu-tang-36-chambers-archived-in-library-of-congress-3206071">他们的首张专辑《Enter The Wu-Tang (36 Chambers)》发行</a>20 周年。该团体自 2015 年以来就没有发布过新唱片。 Wu-Tang Clan 最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-wu-tang-clan-book-legacy-comes-encased-400-pound-steel-chamber-3371093">透露了他们的书<em>《Legacy》</em>的定制钢室</a>。它的售价为 360,000 美元（298,872 英镑），全球仅有 36 辆。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦</a>最近还透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-dylan-is-a-fan-of-wu-tang-clan-and-eminem-3369438">他是这个家族的粉丝</a>，也是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">阿姆的粉丝，</a>称赞他们“对文字和语言的感觉”，并喜欢“任何与我的愿景相似的人”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghostface-killah-announces-new-memoir-rise-of-a-killah-3550391">Ghostface Killah 宣布新回忆录《Rise Of A Killah》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
